	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok, I like many other Iksar Sk's sought after these for a long...... long time.&nbsp;&nbsp;I camped for Zorash in the Overthere on numerous occasions to no avail.  Finally I broke down and went to Iceclad around level 30, leveled up to 35 then camped the Rygor orcs with various groups until I got their greaves.  Since that time I have spent many days in the Dreadlands gaining xp and leveling quite nice, now I'm level 42.  On a trip back into the Overthere to help out a guild member, I just happen to swing by the Sarnak ruins for old times sake and guess who is there staring at me....... Zorash.  I quickly dropped back, engulfed him in Darkness then fear kited him to his death.  I wasn't planning on getting the boots but; there they were..... I couldn't believe it so, I looted those bad boys and went back to Cab to claim my prize.  I know that they don't have the stats that the Rygor do but; I had to have them for my own personal satisfaction. Having the luck to get them now is some kind of sick joke<br>    <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Feb 22 09:23:28 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
